item.title: How does ham work?
item.dc:creator: @n0vamage n0vamage
item.description:
@n0vamage wrote:

you right click on the server name or ip and click copy ip then go to moparscape and click file “new server” then ctrl, v and click ok if it has a port u go to moparscape again go to file and click “new port” and then go to “enter” type ur name and password and click login and if the server is up u will be logging into it
